HOW WE USE PERSONAL INFORMATION
We use personal information to:
Provide our Service
, including to:
Operate the App, the Site and our business;
Create and maintain your account;
Process your payments and manage your subscriptions;
Maintain and improve the App, the App’s features, and the Service;
Develop new products and services;
Communicate with you about the App by sending you push notifications or text messages with announcements, updates, security alerts, and support and administrative messages, if you have enabled that functionality;
Provide support for the App and Site, and respond to your requests, questions and feedback;
Prevent fraud, criminal activity, or misuses of our Service, and to ensure the security of our IT systems, architecture, and networks; and
Comply with legal obligations and legal process and to protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property, and/or that of our affiliates, you, or other third parties.
Direct marketing.
We may send you direct marketing communications as permitted by law, including, but not limited to, notifying you of feature releases or providing content that we think may be of interest to you. You may opt out of our email, push or text-message marketing communications as described in the “
Opt out of marketing communications
” section below. Please note that we may periodically send you transactional emails even after you opt out of direct marketing.
