RISE has users located across the globe. We are headquartered in the United States with services providers that operate in other countries. We may transfer your personal information to the United States and other countries which may not have the same data protection laws as your home country or territory, but we will protect your personal information in accordance with this Privacy Policy, or as otherwise disclosed to you.
